    Class Description
    GameLobby
    Class which displays the game lobby where the game takes place
    Help
    Class that opens a window where you can read the user manual
    LogIn
    Class which makes the log in scene.
    MainMenu
    Class thats crates the main menu which contains several buttons for further choices
    MainScene
    Class which sets scenes
    MyPage
    Class thats creates and displays the MyPage, where you can view your avatar, and change the avatar and password
    Options
    Class that create and opens a popup window where you can turn on/off the music
    Results
    Class thats show the result of the game after a game is playes
    Scenes
    Abstract class that makes the foundation of all the scenes
    SignUp
    Signup Scene where user can register
